    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Springfield <sic>ill</sic></placeName>
                <date>Jay 26 5626</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <addressee>Rev Mr Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(center)indent(1)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p>
                <add>Hebrew</add>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Address</p>
            <p>Care of <persName>Mess Gottlieb &amp; Myers</persName></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Springfield Ill.</placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">I</p>
            <p>A few weeks ago I have notified you<lb/> that I am here in <placeName>Ka.
                    C.</placeName> and<lb/> I didn't get an answer from<lb/> you, but I think that
                the<lb/> letter didn't reach you<lb/> as it was sent in a private way<lb/> so I am
                taking the liberty<lb/> to inform you that I am in <placeName>C.</placeName><lb/>
                Don't mind me bothering you<lb/> and asking <del>for an</del> to respond<lb/> as I
                have nobody except you<lb/> and I hope that a similar<lb/> accident wouldn't happen<lb/>
                <del>any more</del> again.</p>
            <p>You know that a durable<lb/> hope causes heart disease.<lb/> The Jews here do not
                have<lb/> any paper may I'll be able<lb/> to bring <del>it in</del> the
                “Occident”<lb/> I have the pleasure to bring<lb/> my family over here.<lb/>
                <sic>at</sic> present I am in <placeName>Cleveland</placeName></p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">II</p>
            <p><persName>Rev Joseph</persName> and all the<lb/> family feeling fine.</p>
            <p>I hope to get a quick <lb/> answer.<lb/> signing my name below<lb/> I remain devoted
                to you<lb/> with my heart and soul<lb/> and with sincerity<lb/> and
                    <sic>truthfullness</sic></p>
            <p>
                <add>Hebrew</add>
            </p>
            <p>
                <persName>Menachem Elia<add>?</add></persName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">Meyer</persName>
                <del>Rushbern.</del>
                <persName role="author">Marcussohn</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
